Package com.att.aro.videocapture

Provides classes for capturing video from the Android Emulator while collecting application trace data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataAtomOutputStream
    Represents an output stream filter that supports the common data types used inside of QuickTime Data Atoms.
    FilterImageOutputStream
    Represents an output stream filter that supports the creation and handling of an ImageOutputStream for use with the DataAtomOutputStream class.
    QuickTimeOutputStream
    Represents a QuickTime video output stream.
    VideoCaptureMacOS  
    VideoCaptureThread
    Represents a process thread for capturing raw images from the Android Emulator.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    QuickTimeOutputStream.VideoFormat
    The VideoFormat enumeration specifies constant values that describe the video formats that are supported by the QuickTimeOutputStream class.
